    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone seeking reliable transportation. While the mechanical components are well-maintained and the car drives smoothly, the exterior shows its age with some visible paint fading and minor scuffs on the bumpers. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the upholstery and some minor staining in the footwells. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for daily use, provided you aren't looking for a perfect cosmetic finish.",
