    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and refined performance. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish that has been regularly waxed, showing only minor road-wear consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is free of tears or significant stains, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment system\u2014operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a documented history of scheduled oil changes and proactive preventative maintenance. The transmission shifts crisply through every gear, and the suspension provides a comfortable, confident ride without any unwanted rattles or vibrations. Equipped with tires showing excellent tread life and a clean title in hand, this car is fully prepared for its next owner to drive away with total peace of mind. It has been smoke-free and garage-kept, ensuring the interior retains a fresh, clean feel.",
      "price": 36500.0,
